{"tid":1545734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<攬炒>惠譽調低香港信貸評級由「AA+」降至「AA」，評級展望「負面」，反映評級有機會再被下調。","createTime":"2019-09-06T04:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:09:35.000Z","uid":59569,"like":120,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"9e31fd8f7f0b85dce068bec6ed2672c6fe29faf0","tid":1545734,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"惠譽下調香港信貸評級 指自治受侵蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3分鐘前<br />\n【Now新聞台】評級機構惠譽下調香港主權評級。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽調低香港信貸評級由「AA+」降至「AA」，評級展望「負面」，反映評級有機會再被下調。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽指出，香港自治受侵蝕，社會事件造成長期損害，預期下半年經濟收縮，全年零增長，又估計本年度的財政盈餘接近零水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=361832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361832&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=c57429dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361832&h=a36920de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=361832</a><br />\n【原Po】<br />\n大家幫忙 開左個頻道 增加前線資源<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1527612/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1527612/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"781f726e09ff06db43d8d892fc2eb4553ccd7daf","tid":1545734,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"h